client.deployment

Class DeploymentManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • client.deployment.DeploymentManager
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FedoraManager

    public abstract class DeploymentManager
extends java.lang.Object
    The abstract class for the deployment manager running on this client host. It checks and configures the software required to run the C-MART VMs. For specific OS's this class should be extended with custom install scripts The current implementation is only FedoraManager
    Author:
    Ji Yang, Andy Turner
